<section class="hero">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="eyebrow" style="color: var(--color-accent);">Communication isn&rsquo;t a soft skill.</p>
    <h1>It&rsquo;s a superpower!</h1>
    <p class="lede" style="color:#dbe3ee;">
      Communication keynote presentations that leave audiences enlightened, empowered, and entertained.
      Acclaimed keynote speaker <a href="/about#dave" style="color:#fff;">Dave Delaney</a> helps leaders
      and teams build clarity, connection, and confidence through <strong>The Communication Edge</strong>
      and <strong>The ADHD Advantage</strong>, delivered with storytelling, humor, and practical tools
      audiences use immediately.
    </p>
    <div class="hero__actions">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Check Availability</a>
      <a href="/workshops" class="btn btn-outline">Workshops Also Available</a>
    </div>
  </div>
